Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.03,0:00:03.28,720PCN,,0,0,0,,IPA这种酒太有名了，好多人都知道
Dialogue: 2,0:00:00.03,0:00:03.28,720PEN,,0,0,0,,Because it's such a popular style most people know
Dialogue: 1,0:00:03.34,0:00:06.44,720PCN,,0,0,0,,或者他们自以为了解IPA的起源
Dialogue: 2,0:00:03.34,0:00:06.44,720PEN,,0,0,0,,or think they know of the origins of the IPA
Dialogue: 1,0:00:06.70,0:00:08.76,720PCN,,0,0,0,,这里是Beer By The Numbers频道的Ryan，字幕翻译给虫
Dialogue: 2,0:00:06.70,0:00:08.76,720PEN,,0,0,0,,Hey this is Ryan from Beer By The Numbers
Dialogue: 1,0:00:08.76,0:00:13.08,720PCN,,0,0,0,,今天带你了解印度淡色艾尔(IPA)这种酒的真实历史与其发展历程
Dialogue: 2,0:00:08.76,0:00:13.08,720PEN,,0,0,0,,and today we're diving into the true history and evolution of the IPA
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.42,0:00:17.93,720PCN,,0,0,0,,关于IPA流传最广的说法是这样讲的
Dialogue: 2,0:00:13.42,0:00:17.93,720PEN,,0,0,0,,So the popular origin story of the IPA goes something like this...
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.43,0:00:21.85,720PCN,,0,0,0,,18世纪晚期到19世纪早期
Dialogue: 2,0:00:18.43,0:00:21.85,720PEN,,0,0,0,,Back in the late 1700s and early 1800s
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.90,0:00:24.60,720PCN,,0,0,0,,英国在印度有广大的殖民地
Dialogue: 2,0:00:21.90,0:00:24.60,720PEN,,0,0,0,,England held a large colonial presence in India
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.96,0:00:29.25,720PCN,,0,0,0,,但士兵、水手和老百姓都超级想喝啤酒
Dialogue: 2,0:00:24.96,0:00:29.25,720PEN,,0,0,0,,But soldiers, sailors and civilians had a huge appetite for beer
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.60,0:00:31.87,720PCN,,0,0,0,,问题是坐船去印度太慢了
Dialogue: 2,0:00:29.60,0:00:31.87,720PEN,,0,0,0,,Trouble was the voyage to India was long
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.93,0:00:33.80,720PCN,,0,0,0,,按照当时的路线，船开到了之后
Dialogue: 2,0:00:31.93,0:00:33.80,720PEN,,0,0,0,,and by the time the ships made it there
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.80,0:00:36.14,720PCN,,0,0,0,,普通的酒都快馊了
Dialogue: 2,0:00:33.80,0:00:36.14,720PEN,,0,0,0,,the traditional beers had spoiled
Dialogue: 1,0:00:36.64,0:00:40.86,720PCN,,0,0,0,,当然这是夸张的说法，但当时在伦敦比较流行的波特黑啤
Dialogue: 2,0:00:36.64,0:00:40.86,720PEN,,0,0,0,,Even when they didn't, the Dark Porter's that were popular at the time in London
Dialogue: 1,0:00:41.37,0:00:44.52,720PCN,,0,0,0,,也真不适合在天气炎热的印度引用
Dialogue: 2,0:00:41.37,0:00:44.52,720PEN,,0,0,0,,weren't quite the ticket in the hot climate of India
Dialogue: 1,0:00:45.13,0:00:49.07,720PCN,,0,0,0,,伦敦Bow酿酒厂的George Hodgson是当时第一位
Dialogue: 2,0:00:45.13,0:00:49.07,720PEN,,0,0,0,,George Hodgson of the Bow Brewery in London was the first person
Dialogue: 1,0:00:49.07,0:00:51.05,720PCN,,0,0,0,,想到解决办法的人
Dialogue: 2,0:00:49.07,0:00:51.05,720PEN,,0,0,0,,to come up with a solution to this problem
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.42,0:00:55.15,720PCN,,0,0,0,,他开始酿造一种叫淡色艾尔的颜色更淡的啤酒
Dialogue: 2,0:00:51.42,0:00:55.15,720PEN,,0,0,0,,He began brewing a lighter style of beer known as Pale Ale
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.58,0:01:00.93,720PCN,,0,0,0,,Hodgson发现酒精浓度高、酒花多可以在长途旅行中防止啤酒腐败
Dialogue: 2,0:00:55.58,0:01:00.93,720PEN,,0,0,0,,Hodgson realized that a high alcohol and hop levels would prevent spoilage on the long journey
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.52,0:01:02.94,720PCN,,0,0,0,,他成功了
Dialogue: 2,0:01:01.52,0:01:02.94,720PEN,,0,0,0,,His process succeeded
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.94,0:01:07.34,720PCN,,0,0,0,,之后他一直垄断印度的啤酒市场五十余年
Dialogue: 2,0:01:02.94,0:01:07.34,720PEN,,0,0,0,,and for about 50 years he held a virtual monopoly in the Indian market
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.09,0:01:11.02,720PCN,,0,0,0,,所以……这故事错在哪呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:01:08.09,0:01:11.02,720PEN,,0,0,0,,So... what exactly is wrong with this story?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.53,0:01:14.58,720PCN,,0,0,0,,呃……就像很多有名的东西起源全归功于一人一样
Dialogue: 2,0:01:11.53,0:01:14.58,720PEN,,0,0,0,,Well... just like any story that gives all the credit to one person
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.58,0:01:16.11,720PCN,,0,0,0,,事情远没有那么简单
Dialogue: 2,0:01:14.58,0:01:16.11,720PEN,,0,0,0,,it's never that simple
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.11,0:01:20.07,720PCN,,0,0,0,,首先英国殖民者遇到的问题是真实存在的
Dialogue: 2,0:01:16.11,0:01:20.07,720PEN,,0,0,0,,It's certainly true that British exporters were experiencing problems
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.07,0:01:22.28,720PCN,,0,0,0,,啤酒在去印度途中的确有保存问题
Dialogue: 2,0:01:20.07,0:01:22.28,720PEN,,0,0,0,,with beer making the journey to India
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.89,0:01:25.64,720PCN,,0,0,0,,很多啤酒到达印度的时候根本没法喝
Dialogue: 2,0:01:22.89,0:01:25.64,720PEN,,0,0,0,,Much of the beer that arrived in India was not fit to drink
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.00,0:01:28.80,720PCN,,0,0,0,,好多酒直接就倒海里了
Dialogue: 2,0:01:26.00,0:01:28.80,720PEN,,0,0,0,,and there were many accounts of beer being dumped into the sea
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.61,0:01:33.88,720PCN,,0,0,0,,酒桶在海上遇到的这个问题根本没法避免
Dialogue: 2,0:01:29.61,0:01:33.88,720PEN,,0,0,0,,There was just no way to prevent the hardships a cask would experience while at sea
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.51,0:01:36.35,720PCN,,0,0,0,,酒桶从英国出发时
Dialogue: 2,0:01:34.51,0:01:36.35,720PEN,,0,0,0,,When they first departed England
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.35,0:01:39.47,720PCN,,0,0,0,,北大西洋的气候可以让啤酒保持在类似酒窖一样的问题
Dialogue: 2,0:01:36.35,0:01:39.47,720PEN,,0,0,0,,the North Atlantic kept the beer at a perfect cellar temperature
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.47,0:01:42.03,720PCN,,0,0,0,,大概在50-55华氏度(10-12.8摄氏度)
Dialogue: 2,0:01:39.47,0:01:42.03,720PEN,,0,0,0,,between 50 and 55 degrees Fahrenheit
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.52,0:01:46.27,720PCN,,0,0,0,,但当船开到赤道附近绕过非洲的时候这温度就保持不住了
Dialogue: 2,0:01:42.52,0:01:46.27,720PEN,,0,0,0,,But that didn't last as the ships neared the equator to pass around Africa
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.27,0:01:49.48,720PCN,,0,0,0,,温暖的气候让酒桶里充满泡沫
Dialogue: 2,0:01:46.27,0:01:49.48,720PEN,,0,0,0,,where the warm seeds rock the cask to a foamy froth
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.90,0:01:52.40,720PCN,,0,0,0,,酒桶能有80华氏度(26.7摄氏度)
Dialogue: 2,0:01:49.90,0:01:52.40,720PEN,,0,0,0,,and were a balmy 80 degrees
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.18,0:01:56.28,720PCN,,0,0,0,,之后啤酒会在经过非洲好望角附近再次降温
Dialogue: 2,0:01:53.18,0:01:56.28,720PEN,,0,0,0,,Then the beer would be chilled again going around the Horn of Africa
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.28,0:01:59.34,720PCN,,0,0,0,,然后到了殖民地以后又升温
Dialogue: 2,0:01:56.28,0:01:59.34,720PEN,,0,0,0,,before heating up again upon arrival to the colony
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.52,0:02:01.93,720PCN,,0,0,0,,经过数十年的尝试与失败
Dialogue: 2,0:01:59.52,0:02:01.93,720PEN,,0,0,0,,Now through decades of trial and error
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.93,0:02:05.18,720PCN,,0,0,0,,几个酿酒厂发现了一种减缓啤酒腐败的方法
Dialogue: 2,0:02:01.93,0:02:05.18,720PEN,,0,0,0,,a few breweries finally found a way to mitigate some spoilage
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.18,0:02:07.88,720PCN,,0,0,0,,并加入了大量有抑制细菌功效的啤酒花
Dialogue: 2,0:02:05.18,0:02:07.88,720PEN,,0,0,0,,and add a lot of bacteria-killing hops
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.32,0:02:13.11,720PCN,,0,0,0,,这虽然无法保证啤酒不会腐败，但至少酒更容易保鲜了
Dialogue: 2,0:02:08.32,0:02:13.11,720PEN,,0,0,0,,This was certainly no guarantee but it did make beer more likely to survive the journey
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.31,0:02:17.53,720PCN,,0,0,0,,就这样，到了1760年，所有酿酒师都知晓了
Dialogue: 2,0:02:13.31,0:02:17.53,720PEN,,0,0,0,,So much so that by 1760, all Brewers were being advised
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.53,0:02:20.68,720PCN,,0,0,0,,酿酒时加入大量酒花是非常重要的
Dialogue: 2,0:02:17.53,0:02:20.68,720PEN,,0,0,0,,that a large helping of hops was an absolute necessity
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.23,0:02:25.63,720PCN,,0,0,0,,这条多放酒花的建议一传十十传百
Dialogue: 2,0:02:21.23,0:02:25.63,720PEN,,0,0,0,,This bit of advice about hops was being widely circulated
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.63,0:02:29.64,720PCN,,0,0,0,,比之前Hodgson淡色艾尔的故事还要早25-30年
Dialogue: 2,0:02:25.63,0:02:29.64,720PEN,,0,0,0,,some 25 to 30 years prior to Hodgson Pale Ales
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.16,0:02:34.62,720PCN,,0,0,0,,同时印度也在开发与波特、世涛口味相同的啤酒
Dialogue: 2,0:02:30.16,0:02:34.62,720PEN,,0,0,0,,In the meantime India was developing a great taste for the same porters and stouts
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.62,0:02:37.44,720PCN,,0,0,0,,这些啤酒在英国很流行，但没那么多酒花
Dialogue: 2,0:02:34.62,0:02:37.44,720PEN,,0,0,0,,that were popular in London, although these were a bit hoppier
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.61,0:02:42.54,720PCN,,0,0,0,,另外尽管Bow酿酒厂不是第一个把含酒花的淡色艾尔运到印度的
Dialogue: 2,0:02:37.61,0:02:42.54,720PEN,,0,0,0,,And although Bow Breweries wasn't the first hoppy Pale Ale to make it to India
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.73,0:02:44.54,720PCN,,0,0,0,,但它的确是最有名的
Dialogue: 2,0:02:42.73,0:02:44.54,720PEN,,0,0,0,,it was certainly the most popular
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.94,0:02:50.01,720PCN,,0,0,0,,但实际上，就算啤酒、加酒花的啤酒在印度很流行
Dialogue: 2,0:02:44.94,0:02:50.01,720PEN,,0,0,0,,But in reality, even though the beer and hoppy Pale Ales became quite popular in India
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.19,0:02:53.90,720PCN,,0,0,0,,你会惊讶的发现它们在印度市场上、世界啤酒史上只是昙花一现
Dialogue: 2,0:02:50.19,0:02:53.90,720PEN,,0,0,0,,it's surprising to learn that the Indian market was never more than a blip
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.90,0:02:55.63,720PCN,,0,0,0,,你会惊讶的发现它们在印度市场上、世界啤酒史上只是昙花一现
Dialogue: 2,0:02:53.90,0:02:55.63,720PEN,,0,0,0,,in the world of beer at the time
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.20,0:03:00.03,720PCN,,0,0,0,,其巅峰时期印度一年只进口一万桶
Dialogue: 2,0:02:56.20,0:03:00.03,720PEN,,0,0,0,,At its height India was only receiving 10,000 barrels a year
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.40,0:03:04.46,720PCN,,0,0,0,,只是来自北美的啤酒的六分之一
Dialogue: 2,0:03:00.40,0:03:04.46,720PEN,,0,0,0,,that was just one-sixth the amount received by North America
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.70,0:03:08.78,720PCN,,0,0,0,,仅仅是来自英国最大一家酒厂的啤酒的十分之一
Dialogue: 2,0:03:04.70,0:03:08.78,720PEN,,0,0,0,,and just 1/10 of the largest single brewery in England
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.94,0:03:12.22,720PCN,,0,0,0,,也就是十万桶
Dialogue: 2,0:03:08.94,0:03:12.22,720PEN,,0,0,0,,which alone turned out 100,000 barrels
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.73,0:03:16.14,720PCN,,0,0,0,,如果说当时淡色艾尔在印度的进口量如此之小
Dialogue: 2,0:03:12.73,0:03:16.14,720PEN,,0,0,0,,Now based on the pretty small export market to India
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.14,0:03:19.52,720PCN,,0,0,0,,那么IPA在精酿啤酒历史上只用一个脚注就够了
Dialogue: 2,0:03:16.14,0:03:19.52,720PEN,,0,0,0,,I think the IPA would have ended up a footnote in brewing history
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.85,0:03:21.77,720PCN,,0,0,0,,但幸运的是，喜欢酒花的人太多了
Dialogue: 2,0:03:19.85,0:03:21.77,720PEN,,0,0,0,,But fortunately for hopheads everywhere
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.77,0:03:27.47,720PCN,,0,0,0,,伯顿到伦敦的新铁路把淡色艾尔酿酒厂和伦敦市场连接起来
Dialogue: 2,0:03:21.77,0:03:27.47,720PEN,,0,0,0,,a new rail line between Burton and London links the Pale Ale breweries with the huge London market
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.12,0:03:31.50,720PCN,,0,0,0,,很快本来打算在印度打的淡色艾尔广告
Dialogue: 2,0:03:28.12,0:03:31.50,720PEN,,0,0,0,,Soon Pale Ales advertised as ready for India
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.61,0:03:35.90,720PCN,,0,0,0,,偶然的机会变成了在英国非常流行的啤酒
Dialogue: 2,0:03:31.61,0:03:35.90,720PEN,,0,0,0,,began being advertised as a popular special occasion beer
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.16,0:03:40.40,720PCN,,0,0,0,,一家酿酒厂甚至说IPA是啤酒中的贵族
Dialogue: 2,0:03:36.16,0:03:40.40,720PEN,,0,0,0,,One brewery even touted IPAs as the beer of the gentry
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.12,0:03:44.78,720PCN,,0,0,0,,这股商业冲击直接让IPA这一款啤酒流行开来
Dialogue: 2,0:03:41.12,0:03:44.78,720PEN,,0,0,0,,It was a commercial hit and this is when the style was born
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.36,0:03:47.72,720PCN,,0,0,0,,而在印度，IPA从来没那么火过
Dialogue: 2,0:03:45.36,0:03:47.72,720PEN,,0,0,0,,IPAs never sold that well in India
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.74,0:03:50.89,720PCN,,0,0,0,,但IPA名字中的India还是继续留在英国的商店标签上
Dialogue: 2,0:03:47.74,0:03:50.89,720PEN,,0,0,0,,but they became a standard bearer in the English market
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.36,0:03:54.16,720PCN,,0,0,0,,从此，IPA加入精酿啤酒家族
Dialogue: 2,0:03:51.36,0:03:54.16,720PEN,,0,0,0,,As India Pale Ales have evolved
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.16,0:04:00.16,720PCN,,0,0,0,,它往下，谱系分为两支，英国IPA和美国IPA
Dialogue: 2,0:03:54.16,0:04:00.16,720PEN,,0,0,0,,the family tree has split into two distinct categories: British and American IPAs
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.80,0:04:06.59,720PCN,,0,0,0,,英国IPA是很适中的啤酒，酒精度约5%，中等酒花
Dialogue: 2,0:04:00.80,0:04:06.59,720PEN,,0,0,0,,British IPAs are modest beer, around 5% alcohol and only moderate hopping
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.97,0:04:11.63,720PCN,,0,0,0,,而美国IPA比较强，酒精度在6-7%
Dialogue: 2,0:04:06.97,0:04:11.63,720PEN,,0,0,0,,American IPAs are stronger, generally between 6 and 7% alcohol
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.63,0:04:14.96,720PCN,,0,0,0,,而且酒花味道和气味很浓烈
Dialogue: 2,0:04:11.63,0:04:14.96,720PEN,,0,0,0,,and showcase intense hop aromas and flavours
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.50,0:04:18.36,720PCN,,0,0,0,,在19世纪，IPA的变化并不大
Dialogue: 2,0:04:15.50,0:04:18.36,720PEN,,0,0,0,,In the 19th century IPAs didn't change much
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.36,0:04:23.90,720PCN,,0,0,0,,直到20世纪，一些世界级大新闻才改变了英国的啤酒风格
Dialogue: 2,0:04:18.36,0:04:23.90,720PEN,,0,0,0,,It wasn't until the 20th century that world events forced a change to the style in England
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.38,0:04:26.35,720PCN,,0,0,0,,为了在一战中节省谷物
Dialogue: 2,0:04:24.38,0:04:26.35,720PEN,,0,0,0,,To save on grain during World War I
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.35,0:04:29.50,720PCN,,0,0,0,,所有的英国啤酒都要求以低浓度酿造
Dialogue: 2,0:04:26.35,0:04:29.50,720PEN,,0,0,0,,all British beers were required to be brewed at a lower strength
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.76,0:04:32.22,720PCN,,0,0,0,,这一规定永远改变了IPA
Dialogue: 2,0:04:29.76,0:04:32.22,720PEN,,0,0,0,,causing a permanent change to IPAs
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.57,0:04:35.84,720PCN,,0,0,0,,在四十年代，风格依然是淡色艾尔
Dialogue: 2,0:04:32.57,0:04:35.84,720PEN,,0,0,0,,By the 1940s the style was about the same as a Pale Ale
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.84,0:04:40.97,720PCN,,0,0,0,,但在很多酒厂，IPA酒精度却比普通淡色艾尔低
Dialogue: 2,0:04:35.84,0:04:40.97,720PEN,,0,0,0,,And in many breweries, the IPA was less alcoholic than their signature Pale Ale
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.63,0:04:45.13,720PCN,,0,0,0,,在美国，禁酒令差点直接扼杀淡色艾尔的生产
Dialogue: 2,0:04:41.63,0:04:45.13,720PEN,,0,0,0,,In America prohibition nearly killed all ale production
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.13,0:04:48.36,720PCN,,0,0,0,,也肯定摧毁了IPA在美国的流形之势
Dialogue: 2,0:04:45.13,0:04:48.36,720PEN,,0,0,0,,and certainly killed the popularity of the IPA in the US
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.98,0:04:52.91,720PCN,,0,0,0,,但在九十年代，IPA在美国西海岸重新崛起
Dialogue: 2,0:04:48.98,0:04:52.91,720PEN,,0,0,0,,But the IPA found new life in the 1990s on the American West Coast
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.12,0:04:56.30,720PCN,,0,0,0,,精酿啤酒酿酒师发现那里气候非常适合啤酒花生长
Dialogue: 2,0:04:53.12,0:04:56.30,720PEN,,0,0,0,,Craft brewers discovered the awesome hop growing climate
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.30,0:04:58.38,720PCN,,0,0,0,,并开始放越来越多的啤酒花
Dialogue: 2,0:04:56.30,0:04:58.38,720PEN,,0,0,0,,and began using more and more hops
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.54,0:05:00.60,720PCN,,0,0,0,,从此美国IPA死而复生
Dialogue: 2,0:04:58.54,0:05:00.60,720PEN,,0,0,0,,revising the all but dead style
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.00,0:05:05.90,720PCN,,0,0,0,,很快西海岸IPA开始挑战加酒花啤酒的极限
Dialogue: 2,0:05:01.00,0:05:05.90,720PEN,,0,0,0,,Soon West Coast IPAs began pushing the envelope of what hoppy beer could be
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.08,0:05:08.36,720PCN,,0,0,0,,到了今天，美国东北部的酿酒师
Dialogue: 2,0:05:06.08,0:05:08.36,720PEN,,0,0,0,,And today Brewers in the northeast of the US
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.36,0:05:12.19,720PCN,,0,0,0,,又推出了新款的东北部IPA
Dialogue: 2,0:05:08.36,0:05:12.19,720PEN,,0,0,0,,are introducing another evolution to the style with the Northeast IPA
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.73,0:05:17.02,720PCN,,0,0,0,,这些啤酒特点是颜色不透明，还带有很强的水果香味
Dialogue: 2,0:05:12.73,0:05:17.02,720PEN,,0,0,0,,These beers are characterized by their hazy color and strong fruit flavors
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.02,0:05:19.12,720PCN,,0,0,0,,来搭配酒花的各种芬芳之感
Dialogue: 2,0:05:17.02,0:05:19.12,720PEN,,0,0,0,,to pair with all that hoppy goodness
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.69,0:05:22.86,720PCN,,0,0,0,,最开始不起眼的IPA只是为了运往殖民地而发明
Dialogue: 2,0:05:19.69,0:05:22.86,720PEN,,0,0,0,,The humble IPA began as an export to a colony
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.88,0:05:26.76,720PCN,,0,0,0,,之后从英国推广到北美，遍及全球
Dialogue: 2,0:05:22.88,0:05:26.76,720PEN,,0,0,0,,It circled the globe that spread from England to North America
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.76,0:05:32.06,720PCN,,0,0,0,,这种啤酒差点在战争中消亡，却又变成精酿啤酒复兴的标识
Dialogue: 2,0:05:26.76,0:05:32.06,720PEN,,0,0,0,,It nearly died as a style and then became the symbol of the craft beer Renaissance
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.40,0:05:37.29,720PCN,,0,0,0,,名字里带个印度，却从未在印度酿造过，这就是IPA
Dialogue: 2,0:05:32.40,0:05:37.29,720PEN,,0,0,0,,All while bearing the name of a country where it was never actually brewed
